:I1.figure description
:I2 refid='gtfigde' pg=major.gtfigde
:p.This tag signals the start of the description for a figure.
The tag is placed after the optional :hp2.&gml.figcap:ehp2. tag
within a figure.
The GML processor automatically adds a colon(&gml.) following
the caption when a figure description is present.
